## All Status Transitions

### Inquiry intake

| From | To | Trigger | File |
|---|---|---|---|
| PENDING | CLARIFICATION_NEEDED | Seller requests clarification | `api/inquiries/[id]/clarify/route.ts` |
| PENDING / CLARIFICATION_ANSWERED | RESPONDED | Seller submits SellerResponse | `api/inquiries/[id]/respond/route.ts` |
| PENDING | DECLINED | Seller declines | `api/inquiries/[id]/decline/route.ts` |

### Specs stage

| From | To | Trigger | Condition |
|---|---|---|---|
| RESPONDED | NEGOTIATING_SPECS | Buyer initiates spec negotiation | — |
| NEGOTIATING_SPECS | SAMPLE_REQUESTED | `progressToSample()` | `canProgressToSample()` passes: all specs agreed, timer not expired |
| NEGOTIATING_SPECS | NEGOTIATING_SPECS | `reopenSpecs()` | Dispute detected in later stage; `specsReopenCount++`, prior price offers voided |

### Sample stage (optional)

| From | To | Trigger | Condition |
|---|---|---|---|
| SAMPLE_REQUESTED | SAMPLE_APPROVED | `approveSample()` | Buyer approves; PRICE_PAYMENT timer created |
| SAMPLE_REQUESTED | SAMPLE_REJECTED | Buyer rejects | — |
| SAMPLE_REQUESTED | NEGOTIATING_PRICE | `skipSample()` | Buyer opts to skip; PRICE_PAYMENT timer created |

### Price + payment stage

| From | To | Trigger | Condition |
|---|---|---|---|
| SAMPLE_APPROVED / NEGOTIATING_PRICE | NEGOTIATING_PRICE | Initial or counter price offer | — |
| NEGOTIATING_PRICE | NEGOTIATING_CONTRACT | `acceptPriceOffer()` (final accept) | `isPricePaymentAgreed()`: all four fields agreed + tranches agreed if PLATFORM_ESCROW |

### Contract stage

| From | To | Trigger | Condition |
|---|---|---|---|
| NEGOTIATING_CONTRACT | DEAL_CREATED | `signContract()` | Both parties signed, or both signal skip intent, or contract timer expires |
| DEAL_CREATED | DealStatus.ACTIVE | `createDealFromInquiry()` | Automatic on Deal record creation |

### Terminal

| From | To | Trigger | Condition |
|---|---|---|---|
| Any active | WITHDRAWN | `withdrawInquiry()` / `sellerWithdraw()` | Party calls withdrawal; `failureReason` + `WithdrawalReason` record written |
| Any active | EXPIRED / FAILED | `processExpiredTimers()` | `NegotiationTimer.deadline < now` AND `paused = false` |
| NEGOTIATING_PRICE | FAILED | Final offer rejected | Counterparty rejects a locked final offer |

