## Stage-Configured Timer Hours

Stage timer durations are configurable per `CountryConfig` via fields on the `Inquiry` model:

```
specsRoundHours       Int   — hours per specs negotiation round
sampleApprovalHours   Int   — hours for sample approval
priceRoundHours       Int   — hours per price negotiation round
contractRoundHours    Int   — hours for contract signing
reorderRoundHours     Int   — hours for reorder negotiation
```

This allows country-specific defaults without code changes — Bangladesh may have different standard negotiation cadences than a future market expansion.
